summary: Little re-texturing I made for myself. Tired of dirty grey low-resolution clothes.
descriptionHtml:
Set of new textures for female fine clothes.

To install simpy copy the Data folder into Skyrim folder over existing one.

To uninstall mod delete modifed files from Data/textures/clothes/fineclothes01 folder of SkyRim.

List of modifed files:


   outfitf.dds  - textures for woman fine clothes
   outfitf_n.dds  - normal map for woman fine clothes
   bootsf.dds  - textures for woman fine boots

Enjoy!
author: MikoYork
